Target marketNationwide Future Executive UL was designed for small- to medium-sized business clients who need help attracting, rewarding and retaining key employees. It can be structured for businesses interested in corporate owned life insurance (COLI) or corporate sponsored, individually owned (CSIO) life insurance solutions.Product detailsMinimum specified amount: $25,000Maximum amount: $8,000,000Fees:Monthly administrative charge is $5 per month current; $10 per month guaranteedCost of insurance chargeRates will be unisex (80% male/20% female) for all underwriting classesRates will be applied to the net amount at risk on a monthly basisPercent of premium expense chargeCurrent:15% up to Target, 2% Excess (year 1)5% up to Target, 2% Excess (years 2 – 10)2% up to Target, 2% Excess (years 11+)Guaranteed:20% up to Target and Excess (years 1 – 5)10% up to Target and Excess (years 6 – 15)6% up to Target and Excess (years 16+)Surrender charge: No charge for full surrender; no current charge for partial surrenders ($25 guaranteed)Underwriting classes and issue ages: Unisex rates are used for all underwriting classes.Simplified Issue (ages 18 - 70)Guaranteed Issue (ages 18 - 70)Nontobacco Preferred Plus (ages 18 - 75)Nontobacco Preferred (ages 18 - 75)Nontobacco Standard (18 - 80)Tobacco Preferred (18 - 75)Tobacco Standard (18 - 80)Death benefit options:Option 1 (level): The death benefit will be the greater of the specified amount or the minimum death benefit required by Section 7702 of the IRS code.Option 2 (increasing): The death benefit will be the greater of the specified amount plus the cash value at the date of death or the minimum death benefit required by Section 7702 of the IRS code.Option 3 (return of premium)1: The death benefit will be the greater of the specified amount plus premiums paid, minus any withdrawals or surrenders, or the minimum death benefit required by Section 7702 of the IRS code.Life insurance test: CVAT and GPTInterest crediting rate: Rate is updated quarterly; 2.00% guaranteedLoan charge rate:Current:2.90% policy years 1 - 102.00% policy years 11+ (wash loans available in years 11+)Guaranteed: 3.50%Key featuresAccumulation or death benefit-focused strategies: Design an accumulation plan to help key employees save more for retirement, a death-benefit-only plan to help clients provide for their loved ones or a hybrid that combines the benefit of bothPreferred group underwriting: Available with both guaranteed-issue or simplified issue underwriting available, based on case parametersGet startedFor more information, contact the Nationwide Business Solutions Group at 1-877-351-8808.NFW-6072AO1Not available in NY, PR or the Virgin Islands.
